  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Activities</strong></span></p>
<p>With so much to see and do in the city, it's great to have the knowledgeable staff here on had with recommendations. From luxury shopping along the <span>via de' Tornabuoni, museum hopping to places like Palazzo Strozzi, the Uffizi Gallery or Palazzo Pitti and exploring the Tuscan countryside, they're always happy to point you in the right direction or help organise activities you'd like to do while you're in Florence. </span></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free high speed WiFi</li>
<li>24 hour room service</li>
<li>Bike hire (payable locally)</li>
<li>Laundry service (payable locally)</li>
<li>Luggage room </li>
<li>Concierge</li>
<li>Garage (payable locally)</li>
<li>Rooftop terrace</li>
<li>Babysitting service (payable locally)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
